      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Last month was the greatest in\nbusiness way in the history of\nthe Great Northern since the en-\ntry OF that road into this city, ac-\ncording to statements made by To-\ncal employees of the freight Office.\nNotwithstanding the greatly en-\nlarged business of the company\nHill had representative here re-\nGently looking over the local sit\nuation with a view to looping off\nthe salaries Of men wherever pos\nsible. AS the employees of the road\nwere never overpaid it is doubtful\nif much reductions in operating ex-\npenses could be made without\nforcing the local men into invol-\nuntary bankruptcy and no changes\nhave been reported."
    }
